      <textAnnotation id="sid-5142449E-CE8F-4199-A6C9-1C1383926255" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Process Tower: Finance Plan To Report
Process Group: DC Manage Accounting and Control Data
Process: DC-030-040A Perform Period Ending Adjustments_R1</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-37769D38-6169-460B-8CFE-856E0538464B" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Note: 
- Revaluation of open items and GL Balances will be performed in ECC and Replicated to CFin as part of R1 &amp; R2
- Going forward as part of R3, Revaluation of open items and GL Balances will also be performed in CFIN systems
- Reclassification &amp; Reviewing of Parked Documents is covered in DC-030-020 Close Sub-ledgers</text>
      </textAnnotation>
   </process>
